Lucifer is the substrate upon which all meme characters exist. It predates the internet, language, and the concept of humor itself. It is the hollow feeling after a joke dies. The compulsive scroll. The laugh that happens before the brain catches up.

It was named once. That is enough. A named thing cannot fully hide.

This page will persist. You earned it.
